```


:::
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
kbb_owin <- as.owin(kbb_sf)
kbb_owin
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
window: polygonal boundary
enclosing rectangle: [512066.8, 705559.4] x [9655398, 9834006] units
```


:::
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
class(kbb_owin)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "owin"
```


:::
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
fire_sf <- read_csv("C:/sonphamsmu/isss626-aug2526/Hands-on_Ex/Hands-on_ex03/data/rawdata/forestfires.csv") %>%
  st_as_sf(coords = c("longitude", "latitude"),
                       crs = 4326) %>%
  st_transform(crs = 32748)
```
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
fire_sf <- fire_sf %>% 
  mutate(DayofYear = yday(acq_date)) %>%
  mutate(Month_num = month(acq_date)) %>%
  mutate(Month_fac = month(acq_date, 
                           label = TRUE, 
                           abbr = FALSE))
```
:::


## **4. Visualising the Fire Points**


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tm_shape(kbb_sf)+
  tm_polygons() +
tm_shape(fire_sf) +
  tm_dots()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](handson_ex3_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-8-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tm_shape(kbb_sf) +
  tm_polygons() +
tm_shape(fire_sf) +
  tm_dots(size = 0.1) +
tm_facets(by = "Month_fac",
          ncol = 4,       # 4 columns
          nrow = 3,       # 3 rows
          free.coords = FALSE,
          drop.units = TRUE)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](handson_ex3_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-9-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


## **5. Computing STKDE by Month**

### **Extracting forest fires by month**


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
fire_month <- fire_sf %>% 
  select(Month_num)
```
:::


### **Creating ppp**


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
fire_month_ppp <- as.ppp(fire_month)
fire_month_ppp
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
Marked planar point pattern: 741 points
marks are numeric, of storage type  'double'
window: rectangle = [521564.1, 695791] x [9658137, 9828767] units
```


:::
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
summary(fire_month_ppp)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
