:::
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(fire_month_owin)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](handson_ex3_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-15-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


### **Computing Spatio-temporal KDE**


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
st_kde <- spattemp.density(fire_month_owin)
summary(st_kde)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
Spatiotemporal Kernel Density Estimate

Bandwidths
  h = 15102.47 (spatial)
  lambda = 0.0304 (temporal)

No. of observations
  741 

Spatial bound
  Type: polygonal
  2D enclosure: [512066.8, 705559.4] x [9655398, 9834006]

Temporal bound
  [1, 12]

Evaluation
  128 x 128 x 12 trivariate lattice
  Density range: [1.233458e-27, 8.202976e-10]
```


:::
:::


### **Plotting the spatio-temporal KDE object**


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
tims <- c(7,8,9,10,11,12)
par(mfcol=c(2,3))
for(i in tims){ 
  plot(st_kde, i, 
       override.par=FALSE, 
       fix.range=TRUE, 
       main=paste("KDE at month",i))
}
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](handson_ex3_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-17-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


